name: Space Dawn
shortDescription: Space Dawn is a demo app built to demonstrate the use of Mutli-Module Clean MVVM Architecture with Jetpack Compose by following Material-3 guidelines along with other MAD libraries such as Dagger-Hilt
longDescription: Space Dawn is a demo app built to demonstrate the use of Mutli-Module Clean MVVM Architecture with Jetpack Compose by following Material-3 guidelines along with other MAD libraries such as Dagger-Hilt
